### =====================================================================
### Wallet API  (base route: api/wallet/)
### TagWalletTxn: 101 Charge, 102 Transfer, 301 ChargeSimPin ...
### TagWallet: 101 Primary
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Charge - add funds to a user's wallet
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/Charge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "amount": 500000
}

### Transfer - user to user
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/Transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "receiverId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "amount": 100000,
  "detail1": "Gift",
  "tagWalletTxn": [102]
}

### Purchase - spend from wallet
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/Purchase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "tag": 209,
  "amount": 50000
}

### ReadTxn - a user's wallet transactions
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/ReadTxn
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Read - wallets
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### ReadByUserId
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/ReadByUserId
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "selectorArgs": {}
}
